========================================================================
  README (LightCount IP traffic counter)                 wjd, oct 2008
========================================================================

  LightCount is an IP traffic counter. It sniffs ethernet packets and
stores average traffic counts for specified IP addresses.

Copyright: Walter Doekes, OSSO B.V., 2008.
Licensing: GPLv3, see COPYING for details.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Getting LightCount
------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Currently, LightCount is only available through SVN. Check out the
latest version using subversion. The repository is here:

https://code.osso.nl/svn/lightcount/trunk/lightcount

------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Installing LightCount
------------------------------------------------------------------------
  See INSTALL.


